reviewText: Vol. 15 is packed with insightful information providing the listening with entertaining monologue, while also providing excellent research studies to back up his points.
I learn so much from these dvds.  I order them everytime they become available and watch them over and over.  If you have health concerns there is a dvd that will help you.
Fascinating review of latest nutrition research with results that are useful. Encourages me to eat better by showing real results from a healthy diet.
